ases\noccur (Class B2). The phase diagram for Classes B0, B1, B2 is determined by\ndominant ground states. Classes A, B0-B2 are described in terms of cosets in\n$\\mathbb{Z}[{\\sqrt[6]{-1}}]$ by the group of units.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2019 17:49:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Apr 2020 14:41:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-28"}
