ll as the free energy as a function of the\nvarious cluster sizes. Overall, this study reports a new active learning scheme\nwith promising strategy to develop accurate force-fields for molecular\nsimulations using extremely sparse training data sets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2019 17:58:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 2 Nov 2019 15:50:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-05"}
