t the problem arises\nbecause our disformal coupling involves a dimensionful parameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2019 20:38:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Sep 2019 04:10:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Nov 2019 03:41:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-11"}
