 and computational efficiency offer great potential in clinical\nretinal vessel segmentation application. Meanwhile, the network could be\nutilized to extract detail information in other biomedical issues\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Sep 2019 06:50:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Dec 2019 13:09:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-19"}
